Package: demingx
Type: Package
Title: Extended Heteroscedastic Deming Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Jan Gleixner', email = 'jan.gleixner+FOSS@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: Provides functions to fit a slope-only heteroscedastic errors-in-variables model, generalizing classical Deming regression by allowing known per-observation variances and intrinsic scatter estimation.
